Langauge Features
    C produces compact and eficient programs
    C most used programming language
    Main Features   
        Efficietn
        Portable
        Powerful and Flexible
        Programmer Oriented
            Efficiente
                Advantage of the cpabilities of current computer
                c programs are fast and compact(similar to asembly)
                programmers can fine-tune programs for maximun speedd or most efficient use of memory
            Portable
                Wrritten on one system can be run on another system whit little or no moddificatin
                a ladder in protability
                compilers are available for many computers architectures
            Linux/Unix comes witth a C compilere
                Compielrs are avaialble for PC
