                Solving phisics and engineering problems and even for FX in movies
            Flexibility
                developet to create all u can image
                games and operating systems
                it is basic for more advanced languages such as C++
                Mobile apps in form of Objective c(iOS)
                Easy to learn because of compactness
                knowledge for practical aplication development very quick and very easy
            Program Oriented
                gives u access to hardware
                enables you to manipualte individual bits of memory
                Manage own memory
                Large selection of operators wich allows you to express youserlf succinctly
                C gives u more freedome, but you are the responsible of errors and mistakes
                large library of useful C functions
                deal with common need of most programmers
            Other Features  
                Low lvl features provided by the Lower level languages
                manage memory representation at bit levelwide variety of bit manipulation operators
                Pointers give direct access to memory
                Support efficient use of Pointers

